original: Ljungberg, Gunnar Åke David, civilingenjör, Alingsås, f. 13/2/09 i Jönköp. av ing. David L. o. Hanna Pettersson. G. 38 m. Margit Persson. Barn: Per f. 40. — Stud:ex. i Jönköp. 28, utex. fr. CTI (E) 32. Praktik v. Jönk. mekaniska verkstad, Elektr. A-B Sivers & Häger i Jönköp. samt Jönköp. gasverk, anst. v. Borås stads elverk 35-36, v. Yngeredsfors Kraft A-B i Mölndal 36-37, chef v. Alingsås stads gas- o. elverk sed. 38.
translated: Ljungberg, Gunnar Åke David, civil engineer, Alingsås, b. 13/2/09 in Jönköp. to engineer David L. and Hanna Pettersson. Married in 1938 to Margit Persson. Children: Per b. 1940. — Completed secondary education in Jönköp. in 1928, graduated from CTI (E) in 1932. Internship at Jönk. Mechanical Workshop, Elektr. A-B Sivers & Häger in Jönköp., and Jönköp. Gasworks. Employed at Borås City Power Plant from 1935-1936, Yngeredsfors Kraft A-B in Mölndal from 1936-1937, became the manager of Alingsås City Gas and Electric Works since 1938.
